com.adobe.fd.cpdf.api

Class ConvertPdfException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.adobe.fd.cpdf.api.ConvertPdfException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public abstract class ConvertPdfException
extends Exception
    An exception class used to indicate that an exception has occurred when converting a PDF document to a PostScript or image file.
    See Also:
